Summary: cigar shaped craft flew into cloud but didn't exit on other side
trends: There have been 10 other sightings in College Station

divs: Sighting DetailsMy sister was sitting outside with a group of toddlers watching them play. She saw a cigar shaped shiny object with no wings fly into a cloud. It was a fairly cloudless day with just a few clouds in the sky. She watched the object fly into a cloud and since the object was strange looking.she watched to see it come out the other side of the cloud, but it never did.
